Package: Rtwitter
Type: Package
Title: R Package for Exploration of Twitter Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Selim Yaman
Maintainer: Selim Yaman <selimyaman26@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains functions to visualize Twitter data. You can see the plots for most retweeted authors, how words associate with each other, from which sources tweets were sent etc. You can pull tweets via different tools (tweepy, twarc2, academicTwitteR or rtweet) as long as the final dataset has text, user_name, and time columns.
